dvdrip: dvdrip (dvd::rip DVD Ripper)
dvdrip:
dvdrip: dvd::rip is a full featured DVD copy program written in Perl. It provides an
dvdrip: easy to use but feature-rich Gtk+ GUI to control almost all aspects of the
dvdrip: ripping and transcoding process. It uses the widely known video processing
dvdrip: swissknife transcode and many other Open Source tools. dvd::rip itself is
dvdrip: licensed under GPL / Perl Artistic License.
